compile and run the code as follows:

$ make GC=<sweep, compact, copy> # chose either one
$ ./mutator 0.5 100 100000
$ ./mutator 0.1 100 100000
$ ./mutator 0.9 100 100000
$ ./mutator 80 10 1000000

for a simple test

$ make test

to clean and leave just the source code

$ make clean

